BT /F2 20 Tf 54 738.00 Td (PDF Utility Platform - Security & Architecture) Tj ET
BT /F2 20 Tf 54 713.00 Td (  Audit) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 680.00 Td (Role: Senior Full-Stack Architect and Lead Security Auditor) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 665.00 Td (Scope: React/Vite frontend, Express/Multer backend, Node-to-Python processing bridge, Python PDF/document) Tj ET
